<i>noun</i>: 경륜 [경뉸] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>경륜 [경뉸]</dt><br>
<dd>1. insight; accumulated experience</dd><br>
<dd>경험을 통해 얻은 판단력이나, 일정한 포부를 가지고 한 계획.</dd><br>
<dd>One's judgment that one has obtained through experience, or one's plan with a specific ambition.</dd><br>
<dd>2. statecraft; statesmanship</dd><br>
<dd>나라를 다스리는 데에 필요한 경험과 능력.</dd><br>
<dd>Experience and competencies required for a person to govern a country.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>